    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to rulers or leaders of clans, tribes, or other groups. The term typically carries the connotation of rulers who are also military leaders.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
